There&#39;s a few ways to suppress these warnings, but none of them can do so only for certain methods or certain types of methods only in an automatic way. You can do something like:

    #pragma warning disable CA1026
    [HttpGet]
    public IActionResult Foo(string str)
    {
        ...
    }
    #pragma warning restore CA1026

But, you&#39;d have to do that on a case by case basis. Any other option, such as `SuppressMessageAttribute` will apply more globally to every method in a particular controller, for example, since it can only go so granular.

